## Content Guidelines

### Real Estate Content Strategy
- ✅ **Location-First**: Always include Centennial Hills, Las Vegas, zip codes
- ✅ **Property Details**: Include bedrooms, bathrooms, square footage, price
- ✅ **Local Amenities**: Reference Red Rock Canyon, local schools, shopping
- ✅ **Market Insights**: Include current market trends and analysis
- ✅ **User Intent**: Focus on buyer/seller needs and questions

### Keyword Strategy
- **Primary**: "Centennial Hills homes", "Las Vegas real estate", "luxury homes"
- **Secondary**: "89135 homes", "89138 homes", "89144 homes", "new construction"
- **Long-tail**: "Centennial Hills luxury homes for sale", "Las Vegas real estate agent"

### Content Types
- **Property Listings**: Individual property pages with rich descriptions
- **Neighborhood Guides**: Area information and local amenities
- **Market Reports**: Monthly/yearly analysis and trends
- **Blog Posts**: SEO-optimized articles about real estate topics
- **About Pages**: Company information and agent profiles

## Technical SEO

### URL Structure
- ✅ **Clean URLs**: `/properties/123-main-street-centennial-hills`
- ✅ **Descriptive Paths**: `/neighborhoods/centennial-hills/luxury-homes`
- ✅ **Consistent Structure**: Use kebab-case for all URLs
- ✅ **Canonical URLs**: Prevent duplicate content issues

### Image Optimization
- ✅ **WebP Format**: Use WebP for better compression
- ✅ **Alt Text**: Descriptive alt text for all property images
- ✅ **Lazy Loading**: Implement lazy loading for performance
- ✅ **Responsive Images**: Multiple sizes for different devices

### Performance
- ✅ **Core Web Vitals**: LCP < 2.5s, FID < 100ms, CLS < 0.1
- ✅ **Page Speed**: Optimize for fast loading times
- ✅ **Mobile-First**: Ensure mobile performance is excellent
- ✅ **SSG Benefits**: Leverage static generation for better SEO

